CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 23, 1958, pg. C1, reads: "On the Outside - Pretty little Thelma J. Kisner of Pittsburgh is not old enough to enter the swimming pool. So, she just sits on the outside, looking through the wire fence and sucking her thumb.  She is two and one-half years old. - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Thelma J. Kisner sucking thumb through chain link fence, looking towards swimming pool
